    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with perfection. The engine starts up every time and the car drives fine, though you may notice some typical wear and tear such as minor interior staining and a few scratches on the exterior body panels. The tires have decent tread left, but some routine maintenance items like a brake service may be needed in the near future. It is a solid, functional vehicle that has been used regularly and priced according to its current cosmetic and mechanical state.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and primary touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is solid, with a complete service history and all features functioning as intended. It represents a great balance of reliability and value for a driver looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this superlative vehicle, currently maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This specimen has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets the highest standards of mechanical excellence and aesthetic integrity. Featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains indistinguishable from its original factory state, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every detail, from the precision-engineered powertrain to the meticulously preserved cabin materials, confirms its status as a premier example of the marque.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere. It smells like new and drives even better! I've babied this thing since day one, and it's always been garaged. If you're looking for perfection, this is it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-level condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for razor-sharp throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. Crucially, the 'Big Three' have been addressed: rod bearings replaced, VANOS system overhauled, and the rear subframe reinforced with a structural epoxy/plate solution. The suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, and the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders. This is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle with no deferred maintenance and absolute mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No scratches or mechanical issues. Full service records available. Clean title.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive care. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or stone chips; even the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state, featuring pristine upholstery that still carries a fresh scent, with every electronic component, button, and driver aid functioning flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, full-service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. It drives with the same precision and smoothness as the day it was first delivered. This is a rare find for a discerning enthusiast who demands a vehicle with no accidents, no smokers, and absolutely no compromises.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits showroom-grade aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly superlative condition, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 44850.0,
